<br>
I was hoping some of you could clear up a few things for me.  I was contemplating fear, and how it can be done.  Below I've posted an image (which I hope shows up) of fear and how I &quot;think&quot; it was done when I've done it.  I didn't get moved to the pull team until about mid flight so a lot of what was actually going on and where it was being pulled from was missed, but this is what I could gather.<br>
<br>
The Blue circle is safe spot of course.  We sat there and the pull team was off to the west pulling things in.  Since there wasn't much room to go further west I'm guessing they were pulling south along the wall.<br>
<br>
Question 1.  Is that so?  I would think it would be done that way simply because along the wall it would attract less attention.<br>
<br>
After we pulled all the mobs we were going to there, we proceeded along the blue line.  Again, remember all of this is fairly vague.  I am thinking we travelled this way because when we parked I could see the portal out sorta in front and to my left.  Also we seemed to be in a &quot;corner&quot; so I'm guessing thats where we were.<br>
<br>
Question 2.  If I'm right, then what areas where they pulling from to here.  Just all out in front?  I noticed a lot of monkeys patrolling around the portal area.<br>
<br>
Next we moved from the Red Dot along the wall and then curved up to the Green Dot, which was an empty building sitting on its east wall.  It was empty.  I could see that bridge thing to the North East, so thats why I put the dot there.  We fought there a while, and then we moved from the Green Dot to the second Green Dot.  We fought golems and such here.  This is where I got moved up to the pull team.<br>
<br>
Question 3.  Where were these golems and Amys coming from.  Everyone kept talking about there being 4 Golems to kill.  I'm interested in where they were being pulled from.<br>
<br>
After that, we moved back to the Green Dot.  We killed a few more things and then we killed that big bone dragon thing.  This guy came out of nowhere.  I was the first one to scream &quot;Oh Shit!&quot; and wet myself because the group was currently fighting something else.<br>
<br>
Question 4.  What was that guys name again?  And where did he come from.  They were talking about him, but from what I gathered he wasn't supposed to just wonder in.  So I'm curious.<br>
<br>
Finally we moved along the Yellow Line.  Thats where we did a whole bunch of glare lords and big black horses.  God I hate those glare lords.  Now at this point everyone was beat, and leaving.  I hated it because they were saying that we only had the Temple and Cazic left.<br>
<br>
Question 5.  Where is this temple they were talking about.  And what all comes from there?<br>
<br>
A few people stayed and some necro went off to pull that temple, and then Cazic showed up, feard me, killed everyone, and the show was pretty much over.  A huge AoF.  Only he is skinny.<br>
<br>
So, if you don't mind, I'd like a few things.<br>
<br>
1. Correct what I am mistaken about here.<br>
2. Show me if you would, another way, or a few others ways to do this.<br>
<br>
Again, I might be off a bit here, because I wasn't sure of my location a few times.  And also Cazic was up, so I'm sure that changes the way its done.  Regardless, I'd like to learn more about how it can be efficiently done.<br>
<br>
Thanks<br>
<br>
